  Locus:
    Page: 18
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Ambition
---
Ambition makes the same mistake concerning power, that avarice makes as to
wealth. She begins by accumulating it as a means of happiness, and finishes
by continuing to accumulate it as an end.
